                        <bindingDesc>
                            <binding contemporary="unknown">
                                <p>Medieval or early modern binding. Brown leather over wooden boards. 3 double raised bands and endbands. Hooked clasp. <locus from="Spine" to="Spine" scheme="other"/>, stamped in gold: <quote>A 233</quote>.</p>
                                <p>
